<h2>Search Using an HTML Form</h2>
<p>Search by event name using the field below.</p>
<form id="search-event-html" method='GET' action='/event'>
    <label for="input-event">Search by Event Name: </label>
    <input type="text" name="event_type" id="input-event_type-html-search">
    
    <input type="submit">
    <a href='/event'><button>Reset</button></a>
</form>

<h2>Updating An Event's Attendance Form</h2>
<p>To update a specific event's attendance select its name from the drop-down menu on the left and input the updated attendance number on the right</p>
<form id="update-event-form-ajax">

    <label for="input-event_type">Event Name: </label>
    <select name="input-event_type" id="mySelect">
